1. *Okean* je najdublji na mestima koja su najudaljenija od kopna. (The *ocean* is the deepest in places farthest from the coast.)
2. More se spaja sa *okeanom* na severu Evrope. (The sea connects with the *ocean* in northern Europe.)
3. Svi putevi vode do *okeana*. (All roads lead to the *ocean*.)
4. *Okeanska* voda sadrži mnogo soli. (The *oceanic* water contains a lot of salt.)
5. Ploviti *okeanima* je uzbudljivo, ali i opasno. (Sailing the *oceans* is exciting but also dangerous.)
6. *Okeanske* struje igraju važnu ulogu u globalnoj klimi. (The *oceanic* currents play an important role in global climate.)
7. Naučnici proučavaju dubine *okeana* i otkrivaju nove vrste. (Scientists study the depths of the *ocean* and discover new species.)
8. *Okeanski* talasi mogu biti vrlo visoki i razorni. (The *oceanic* waves can be very high and destructive.)
9. Pejzaž *okeanskog* dna je jedinstven i fascinantan. (The landscape of the *oceanic* floor is unique and fascinating.)
10. *Okean* je ogromno prostranstvo vode koje pokriva većinu planete. (The *ocean* is a vast expanse of water that covers most of the planet.)